-- Multi-branch nested partiality — e.g. `W (JUST 1) NOTHING TRUE` has no
-- arm — must be flagged non-exhaustive, with a minimal wildcard cover as
-- the suggestion set, and the analysis must TERMINATE fast. This exact
-- shape has been through three lives: it originally HUNG the type-checker
-- (self-referential constraints from the constructor-keyed variable
-- recycling), then terminated but went silently UNDETECTED (the old
-- refinement normalization unioned uncovered disjuncts into one
-- constraint set), and is now correctly detected by the sequential
-- residual-set analysis. It pins all three properties.
DECLARE W
  HAS a IS A MAYBE OF NUMBER
      b IS A MAYBE OF MAYBE OF NUMBER
      c IS A BOOLEAN

GIVEN w IS A W
GIVETH A NUMBER
f w MEANS
  CONSIDER w
  WHEN W (JUST p) (JUST (JUST q)) FALSE THEN 1
  WHEN W NOTHING NOTHING TRUE THEN 0
